Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.99,0:00:37.03,Default,,0,0,0,,WHY DO YOU CONTINUE TO FORGET US? \NWHY HAVE YOU ABANDONED US FOR SO LONG?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.12,0:00:38.24,Default,,0,0,0,,God,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.33,0:00:42.54,Default,,0,0,0,,do we really
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.62,0:00:44.75,Default,,0,0,0,,have to be pure?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.13,0:00:52.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.22,0:00:56.05,Default,,0,0,0,,My father said that those who do not \Nfollow your commands
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.14,0:00:58.10,Default,,0,0,0,,shall be punished.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.02,0:01:03.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Even if they're an angel.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.15,0:01:08.06,Default,,0,0,0,,A person like me
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.15,0:01:10.44,Default,,0,0,0,,could never understand your will.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.78,0:01:15.57,Default,,0,0,0,,But I feel that your kingdom in heaven
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.65,0:01:17.99,Default,,0,0,0,,is very far away.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.03,0:01:20.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Anne!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.58,0:01:24.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Help me get dinner ready!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.58,0:01:26.92,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm coming! I'm coming!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.05,0:01:41.10,Default,,0,0,0,,I felt burdened
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.93,0:01:44.64,Default,,0,0,0,,to know that
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.89,0:01:49.27,Default,,0,0,0,,you sit in heaven
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.77,0:01:54.03,Default,,0,0,0,,and watch us.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.45,0:03:28.45,Default,,0,0,0,,THE LIGHT OF DAWN
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.58,0:03:29.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Jehovah.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.75,0:03:33.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Restore us to yourself,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.75,0:03:35.75,Default,,0,0,0,,oh, Lord,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.09,0:03:38.67,Default,,0,0,0,,that we may return,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.26,0:03:42.26,Default,,0,0,0,,renew our days
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.22,0:03:46.47,Default,,0,0,0,,as of old.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.44,0:03:56.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, it's like this, Mr. Priest.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.27,0:03:58.48,Default,,0,0,0,,That's it!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.57,0:04:00.49,Default,,0,0,0,,It's like me and my brother.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.53,0:04:04.41,Default,,0,0,0,,We've always been together since we were kids.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.49,0:04:06.62,Default,,0,0,0,,We helped each other out.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.58,0:04:11.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Our teamwork makes us unbeatable
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.08,0:04:13.75,Default,,0,0,0,,on the battlefield. Right?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.88,0:04:17.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah. We can read each other's minds.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.59,0:04:20.88,Default,,0,0,0,,He's the only one I can trust to have my back.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.97,0:04:25.64,Default,,0,0,0,,I'd never trade our relationship for silver. \NRight, brother?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.72,0:04:29.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course not, brother. Well, it depends on how much.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.68,0:04:34.02,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a bond of brotherhood!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.94,0:04:36.94,Default,,0,0,0,,-What do you think? \N-What do you think?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.69,0:04:39.82,Default,,0,0,0,,-Did we get it right? \N-Did we get it right?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.98,0:04:43.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, who knows?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.82,0:04:47.91,Default,,0,0,0,,It's completely different from what I imagine love to be.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.74,0:04:52.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Listen, you priest.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.08,0:04:55.42,Default,,0,0,0,,You've never been on the battlefield.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.50,0:04:57.75,Default,,0,0,0,,So, you don't understand \Nhow amazing this is!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.84,0:05:00.42,Default,,0,0,0,,A union formed in a moment of life or death!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.50,0:05:02.72,Default,,0,0,0,,You'd never be able to do it yourself!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.76,0:05:07.22,Default,,0,0,0,,I think it's wonderful.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.76,0:05:09.51,Default,,0,0,0,,It must be something very valuable
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.60,0:05:11.93,Default,,0,0,0,,to you two brothers.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.18,0:05:14.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Well then.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.10,0:05:17.15,Default,,0,0,0,,If I were to enter the battlefield,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.81,0:05:20.73,Default,,0,0,0,,would you have my back?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.78,0:05:24.03,Default,,0,0,0,,What? What are you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.36,0:05:26.82,Default,,0,0,0,,I can do it because he's my brother.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.91,0:05:29.62,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't trust my back to a drunk priest!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.24,0:05:32.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Right?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.75,0:05:34.25,Default,,0,0,0,,That's why it's not the same.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.33,0:05:39.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Excuse me, could you explain it \Nin a way I can understand?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.25,0:05:42.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Well then, what about you?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.63,0:05:44.59,Default,,0,0,0,,You really like booze.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.67,0:05:47.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe that's "love."
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.97,0:05:49.22,Default,,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.72,0:05:53.47,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not that I love booze.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.56,0:05:54.64,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.73,0:05:55.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Then stop drinking.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.02,0:05:57.39,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.48,0:05:59.90,Default,,0,0,0,,He doesn't make sense.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.98,0:06:01.98,Default,,0,0,0,,You like things that don't make sense?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.07,0:06:04.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Then how about this?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.36,0:06:08.07,Default,,0,0,0,,The veterans still talk about it even today.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.70,0:06:11.99,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a story about when \Nwe attacked a ship in the Faroes.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.87,0:06:15.70,Default,,0,0,0,,There was one warrior on that ship.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.29,0:06:19.21,Default,,0,0,0,,He had incredible strength.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.09,0:06:25.17,Default,,0,0,0,,We attacked him together,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.26,0:06:27.97,Default,,0,0,0,,but he beat 30 of our men with his bare hands!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.05,0:06:29.13,Default,,0,0,0,,His bare hands!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.47,0:06:33.85,Default,,0,0,0,,In the end, we killed him.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.93,0:06:38.19,Default,,0,0,0,,But when it was time to count our losses, \Nwe found that no one had died.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.27,0:06:41.02,Default,,0,0,0,,I wonder what that was all about.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.11,0:06:44.07,Default,,0,0,0,,That guy was carrying a sword, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.15,0:06:47.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe he thought we were no match for him.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.15,0:06:49.20,Default,,0,0,0,,If so, it angers me.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.28,0:06:51.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Where are his manners as a warrior?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.99,0:06:56.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Did he
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.12,0:06:58.87,Default,,0,0,0,,do anything else?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.71,0:07:01.33,Default,,0,0,0,,What's his name?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.42,0:07:04.17,Default,,0,0,0,,I-- I don't know his name.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.96,0:07:06.96,Default,,0,0,0,,I guess
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.05,0:07:11.30,Default,,0,0,0,,weirdos are drawn to each other.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.39,0:07:14.35,Default,,0,0,0,,That guy said some strange things, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.43,0:07:17.93,Default,,0,0,0,,"A true warrior doesn't need a sword."
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.02,0:07:19.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Something like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.61,0:07:31.49,Default,,0,0,0,,What? Priest?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.57,0:07:34.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey. Where are you going? Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.04,0:07:41.04,Default,,0,0,0,,What is it, priest?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.12,0:07:43.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Did we get it right? Was that "love?"
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.72,0:07:57.18,Default,,0,0,0,,A warrior... A true...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.72,0:07:59.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Doesn't need a sword...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.69,0:08:09.74,Default,,0,0,0,,A true warrior...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.91,0:08:25.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't complain to me about the weather!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.17,0:08:29.63,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm a sailor. The weather on top of a hill
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.71,0:08:32.59,Default,,0,0,0,,is not my area of expertise.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.18,0:08:36.68,Default,,0,0,0,,No one could have predicted that it was \Ngoing to snow this much
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.76,0:08:38.06,Default,,0,0,0,,at the start of winter.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.76,0:08:41.85,Default,,0,0,0,,That's not what I'm trying to say.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.93,0:08:45.60,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm trying to say that luck is no longer on your side.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.77,0:08:49.48,Default,,0,0,0,,We changed our route to beat the winter snows, \Nand now we end up like this!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.57,0:08:52.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Your soldiers are also worried.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.90,0:08:56.99,Default,,0,0,0,,My men have been to hell and back.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.24,0:09:00.29,Default,,0,0,0,,For them, this is nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.66,0:09:03.71,Default,,0,0,0,,They're following their orders with no hesitation. See?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.08,0:09:10.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Turn back. It'd be crazy to try to cross Mercia!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.46,0:09:16.59,Default,,0,0,0,,If we're going to walk through the snow, \Nwe'll have to leave our plunder behind.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.97,0:09:18.64,Default,,0,0,0,,My men aren't going to like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.81,0:09:21.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Either way,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.18,0:09:23.48,Default,,0,0,0,,we can't camp out in the open tonight.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.40,0:09:27.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Askeladd.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.69,0:09:29.69,Default,,0,0,0,,We're ready.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.77,0:09:31.11,Default,,0,0,0,,We can go.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.19,0:09:32.23,Default,,0,0,0,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.07,0:09:35.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Askeladd.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.49,0:09:38.37,Default,,0,0,0,,When luck's not on your side,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.45,0:09:40.74,Default,,0,0,0,,no matter what you do, \Nit's going to backfire.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.83,0:09:42.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Ragnar.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.20,0:09:46.58,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you hesitating for?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.09,0:09:53.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Attacking and plundering villages
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.13,0:09:56.63,Default,,0,0,0,,is a tradition for us Norsemen.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.64,0:10:07.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Our father, who art in heaven,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.56,0:10:11.57,Default,,0,0,0,,give us this day our daily bread.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.82,0:10:14.40,Default,,0,0,0,,And forgive us our debts,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.48,0:10:16.70,Default,,0,0,0,,as we also have forgiven our debtors.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.74,0:10:19.36,Default,,0,0,0,,And lead us not into temptation,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.45,0:10:22.03,Default,,0,0,0,,but deliver us from evil.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.12,0:10:24.29,Default,,0,0,0,,For thine is the kingdom,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.37,0:10:26.75,Default,,0,0,0,,and the power, and the glory, \Nfor ever and ever.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.62,0:10:28.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Amen.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.75,0:10:30.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Amen.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.92,0:10:37.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Father!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.38,0:10:41.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Why do we always pray?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.35,0:10:46.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Because Jesus told us to do so.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.10,0:10:48.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Jesus is always right.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.73,0:10:51.52,Default,,0,0,0,,What happens if we don't pray?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.61,0:10:56.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, the unbelievers are going to go to hell.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.19,0:10:57.53,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.61,0:11:01.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Hell is a scary place where the devil lives.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.95,0:11:04.03,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't want to see the devil, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.45,0:11:07.29,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm scared of the devil.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.37,0:11:09.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah. I'm scared of him, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.87,0:11:13.79,Default,,0,0,0,,But good kids who pray can go to heaven.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.88,0:11:15.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't forget.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.59,0:11:20.88,Default,,0,0,0,,It doesn't make sense.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.18,0:11:25.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Everyone's going to be taken to heaven \Nor hell soon?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.60,0:11:29.23,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't want our family to get separated.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.31,0:11:31.10,Default,,0,0,0,,But, Father,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.19,0:11:35.36,Default,,0,0,0,,why did God decide to pass judgment \Non the world all of a sudden?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.65,0:11:37.23,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not sudden.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.32,0:11:39.61,Default,,0,0,0,,It was decided a long time ago
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.69,0:11:43.57,Default,,0,0,0,,that it would happen a thousand years \Nafter the resurrection of Jesus.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.70,0:11:46.83,Default,,0,0,0,,In other words, 20 years later.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.08,0:11:57.30,Default,,0,0,0,,When God passes judgment, \Nall evil men are going to hell.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.96,0:11:59.13,Default,,0,0,0,,I know!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.21,0:12:01.09,Default,,0,0,0,,The Danes are the evil men!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.17,0:12:03.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah! They're really evil.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.05,0:12:07.43,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sure God knew that \Npeople like them
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.51,0:12:09.35,Default,,0,0,0,,would turn up.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.89,0:12:14.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Listen. Make sure you follow God's commandments.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.19,0:12:16.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Anne.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.65,0:12:19.78,Default,,0,0,0,,I have to pee.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.62,0:12:32.58,Default,,0,0,0,,What am I going to do? I'm so scared of the devil!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.73,0:12:56.31,Default,,0,0,0,,But it's so pretty!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.73,0:12:59.36,Default,,0,0,0,,I put it on again.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.82,0:13:03.70,Default,,0,0,0,,I wonder how much this ring costs.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.78,0:13:05.86,Default,,0,0,0,,I wonder if God would forgive me
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.95,0:13:08.49,Default,,0,0,0,,if I paid for it.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.83,0:13:16.50,Default,,0,0,0,,The devil must have tempted me.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.84,0:13:27.09,Default,,0,0,0,,I shouldn't have gone to the market \Nwhen I don't have any money.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.10,0:13:32.43,Default,,0,0,0,,I bet bad children like me
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.52,0:13:35.77,Default,,0,0,0,,will be sent to hell \Non the day of judgment.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.02,0:13:40.94,Default,,0,0,0,,I bet I'm going to be the only one \Nin my family
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.36,0:13:44.07,Default,,0,0,0,,who's not going to heaven.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.83,0:14:00.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Wow!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.54,0:14:03.46,Default,,0,0,0,,It looks so pretty on my left hand, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.47,0:14:11.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Who are they?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.52,0:14:17.94,Default,,0,0,0,,What's wrong with your face?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.94,0:14:21.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Me, too! Me, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.15,0:14:25.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Weren't you listening just now?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.82,0:14:28.70,Default,,0,0,0,,If you're not good, \NGod is going to punish you--
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.20,0:14:37.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.21,0:14:38.96,Default,,0,0,0,,I found dinner.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.00,0:14:44.92,Default,,0,0,0,,BUT THOU HAST UTTERLY REJECTED US; \NTHOU ART VERY WROTH AGAINST US.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.51,0:14:49.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Everyone!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.01,0:14:51.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Run away!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.93,0:14:55.10,Default,,0,0,0,,The village is under attack!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.18,0:14:56.18,Default,,0,0,0,,The Danes
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.27,0:14:57.89,Default,,0,0,0,,are attacking the village!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.10,0:15:00.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Shut up!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.32,0:15:09.45,Default,,0,0,0,,It's so warm here. I feel alive again.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.53,0:15:12.32,Default,,0,0,0,,What's with this family? \NThere's so many kids.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.16,0:15:17.29,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you want all of a sudden?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.37,0:15:20.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Milk porridge with barley and a bit of jerky.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.83,0:15:22.92,Default,,0,0,0,,It has onions in it.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.84,0:15:26.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey. Get everything that can be used \Nas a weapon.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.46,0:15:27.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.39,0:15:38.64,Default,,0,0,0,,This is terrible. You're eating some bad food.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.31,0:15:43.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey! What's wrong with you?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.98,0:15:45.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't waste food!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.65,0:15:47.86,Default,,0,0,0,,-Mom! \N-You're going to be punished for this!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.07,0:15:56.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you okay? Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.20,0:15:59.83,Default,,0,0,0,,How do you say it in English again?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.91,0:16:02.04,Default,,0,0,0,,"Give me all your food."
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.12,0:16:04.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes. That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.42,0:16:07.21,Default,,0,0,0,,-Hey! \N-Hey, old man.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.01,0:16:14.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Give me all your food. I'll kill you.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.02,0:16:20.56,Default,,0,0,0,,And this one.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.44,0:16:25.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that all?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.27,0:16:28.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Put it there.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.73,0:16:31.53,Default,,0,0,0,,If we count two kids as one adult, \Nthat makes 50 people.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.61,0:16:34.78,Default,,0,0,0,,That means there's only enough food for 50 \Nto last the winter.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.75,0:16:43.21,Default,,0,0,0,,It won't be enough for 104 soldiers.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.00,0:16:48.84,Default,,0,0,0,,What am I going to do?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.92,0:16:51.84,Default,,0,0,0,,They captured everyone! What am I going to do?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.01,0:16:57.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Priest!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.81,0:17:02.10,Default,,0,0,0,,You're the prince's teacher.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.18,0:17:04.60,Default,,0,0,0,,That makes you our guest.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.90,0:17:07.52,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll forgive you just once.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.61,0:17:09.86,Default,,0,0,0,,But if you get in our way again,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.94,0:17:11.65,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm going to kill you on the spot.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.90,0:17:15.28,Default,,0,0,0,,I hate priests, to be honest.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.20,0:17:20.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you guys
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.70,0:17:23.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Danes?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.58,0:17:26.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Do any of you speak our language?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.22,0:17:38.34,Default,,0,0,0,,I beg you! Leave us half of the food!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.43,0:17:41.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Please, at least leave us half of the food.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.26,0:17:44.18,Default,,0,0,0,,If we have half, we can make it through the winter!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.06,0:17:50.73,Default,,0,0,0,,I have a baby! Please!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.69,0:17:55.57,Default,,0,0,0,,A baby? That's rough.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.24,0:18:03.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't worry. I made sure to think about you.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.29,0:18:06.21,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't have to worry about making it through \Nthe winter.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.67,0:18:09.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Really? Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.25,0:18:11.67,Default,,0,0,0,,It's true.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.30,0:18:16.42,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't need to worry about making it through \Nthis winter or any winters to come.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.55,0:18:20.51,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm going to release you from your suffering.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.93,0:18:29.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Askeladd. They're civilians.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.19,0:18:34.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Even if I let them live, I don't have any food \Nto feed them.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.90,0:18:37.45,Default,,0,0,0,,If even one of them escapes,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.53,0:18:40.45,Default,,0,0,0,,they're going to tell the enemy that we're here.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.53,0:18:42.37,Default,,0,0,0,,We can't allow that to happen.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.66,0:18:46.00,Default,,0,0,0,,How did it go? Were you able to dig the hole?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.08,0:18:49.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah. We can fit 62 if we cram them in.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.67,0:18:50.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Askeladd!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.42,0:18:53.80,Default,,0,0,0,,They're Christians!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.59,0:18:56.09,Default,,0,0,0,,So what?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.71,0:19:00.18,Default,,0,0,0,,This is what's best for the prince.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.64,0:19:01.64,Default,,0,0,0,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.76,0:19:03.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Any more questions?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.56,0:19:06.02,Default,,0,0,0,,No more questions.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.27,0:19:07.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Very well.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.68,0:19:08.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Men!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.65,0:19:12.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Kill them.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.84,0:21:00.09,Default,,0,0,0,,God.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.88,0:21:06.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you watching?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.31,0:21:17.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Did my father,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.86,0:21:20.32,Default,,0,0,0,,my mother, my grandfather,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.40,0:21:22.40,Default,,0,0,0,,my brothers, and my sisters
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.82,0:21:28.99,Default,,0,0,0,,arrive over there?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.92,0:21:48.05,Default,,0,0,0,,You aren't going to call me there too, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.51,0:21:50.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Right?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.89,0:21:53.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Because
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.69,0:21:58.60,Default,,0,0,0,,I feel elated now.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.19,0:22:06.82,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't believe
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.90,0:22:10.66,Default,,0,0,0,,such evil people exist.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.99,0:22:13.70,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't believe
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.79,0:22:17.12,Default,,0,0,0,,there are people who aren't afraid \Nof your punishment.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.04,0:22:24.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Just like the moment I stole this ring.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.38,0:22:27.97,Default,,0,0,0,,I feel
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.01,0:22:33.68,Default,,0,0,0,,elated now.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.12,0:00:38.24,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,神様。
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.33,0:00:42.54,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,どうしてもアタシたちは
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.62,0:00:44.75,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,清くなければいけませんか？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.13,0:00:52.30,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,本当ですか？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.22,0:00:56.05,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,あなたの言いつけを守らない者は
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.14,0:00:58.10,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,天使でさえ罰せられると…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.02,0:01:03.68,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,父ちゃんが言ってました。
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.15,0:01:08.06,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,アタシのような者に、
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.15,0:01:10.44,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,あなたの思し召しはわかりません。
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.78,0:01:15.57,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,ただ、アタシにはあなたの天の国は
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.65,0:01:17.99,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,とても遠くに感じられます
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.03,0:01:20.37,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,アーン！
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.58,0:01:24.50,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,晩の支度を手伝っとくれ
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.58,0:01:26.92,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,行く！今行く！
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.05,0:01:41.10,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,あなたが…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.93,0:01:44.64,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,あなたが天に座し、
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.89,0:01:49.27,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,私たちを見ていらっしゃることが…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.77,0:01:54.03,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,アタシには重荷でした
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.58,0:03:29.62,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,エホバよ…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.75,0:03:33.67,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,ねがわくは我らをして
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.75,0:03:35.75,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,汝に歸らしめ給え…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.09,0:03:38.67,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,われら歸るべし
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.26,0:03:42.26,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,我らの日を新にして、
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.22,0:03:46.47,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,昔日の日のごとくならしめ給え
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.44,0:03:56.57,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,あー、つまり神父さんよ。
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.27,0:03:58.48,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,アレだ。
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.57,0:04:00.49,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,オレとこの兄貴がそうだ
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.53,0:04:04.41,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,ガキの頃から何をする時も一緒！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.49,0:04:06.62,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,お互い助け合ってやってきた。
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.58,0:04:11.00,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,あ～…戦場での連携プレーじゃ
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.08,0:04:13.75,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,誰にも負けねェぜ。なァ？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.88,0:04:17.50,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,おおとも。ツーカーよ。
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.59,0:04:20.88,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,オレが背中を預けられんのはコイツだけよ
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.97,0:04:25.64,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,この信頼関係は銀にゃあ代えらんねェよな。兄者！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.72,0:04:29.85,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,あたりきよ弟！まァ金額によるがな！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.68,0:04:34.02,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,兄弟のきず
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.94,0:04:36.94,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,どうよ～？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.69,0:04:39.82,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,あたり？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.98,0:04:43.28,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,さァ…どうなんでしょうね
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.82,0:04:47.91,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,私の想像する愛とは全然違いますけど
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.74,0:04:52.04,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,あのなァ神父！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.08,0:04:55.42,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,お前は戦場に出たことねーから
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.50,0:04:57.75,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,このスゴさがわかんねンだよっ！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.84,0:05:00.42,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,生死の最中のコンビネーション！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.50,0:05:02.72,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,できるか！？お前に！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.76,0:05:07.22,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,素晴らしいことだとは思います。
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.76,0:05:09.51,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,あなた方兄弟にとっては
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.60,0:05:11.93,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,かけがえのないものなのでしょうね
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.18,0:05:14.18,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,では
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.10,0:05:17.15,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,私が戦場に立ったとして…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.81,0:05:20.73,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,あなたは私の背後を守って下さいますか？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.78,0:05:24.03,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,あァ？何言ってんだ？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.36,0:05:26.82,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,兄者とだからやれるんだっつーの！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.91,0:05:29.62,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,酒漬け坊主に背中任せられっかよ！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.24,0:05:32.66,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,でしょう…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.75,0:05:34.25,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,だからちがう
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.33,0:05:39.17,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,カーッ！すみませんがわかるように言ってくれやがりませんかねェ…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.25,0:05:42.25,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,そいじゃアさー。それはどーなんだよ
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.63,0:05:44.59,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,アンタやたら酒好きだ。
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.67,0:05:47.09,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,その酒は“アイ”なんじゃねェのかい？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.97,0:05:49.22,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,違います。
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.72,0:05:53.47,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,それに私は酒が好きなわけではありません
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.56,0:05:54.64,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,は！？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.73,0:05:55.93,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,じゃ飲むなよ
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.02,0:05:57.39,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,すみません
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.48,0:05:59.90,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,コイツワケわからん
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.98,0:06:01.98,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,ワケわからんのがいいのか？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.07,0:06:04.23,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,じゃあこんなのはどうだ
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.36,0:06:08.07,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,古株の間じゃ今でも話にのぼる。
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.70,0:06:11.99,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,昔オレらがフェローで船を襲ったときのことだ…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.87,0:06:15.70,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,その船には戦士がひとり乗っててな
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.29,0:06:19.21,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,コレがもう、めっぽう強かった
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.09,0:06:25.17,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,オレらは総出でかかったんだが、そいつひとりに30人が
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.26,0:06:27.97,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,あっちゅー間に素手で叩き伏せられた。
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.05,0:06:29.13,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,素手だぞ？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.47,0:06:33.85,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,結局そいつはオレらが仕留めたが、
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.93,0:06:38.19,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,あとで損害を調べたら不思議なことに死者がいねェ。
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.27,0:06:41.02,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,なんだったんだろーなありゃ…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.11,0:06:44.07,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,野郎たしか剣を帯びてたよなァ？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.15,0:06:47.07,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,やっぱオレらナメられてたんだろうか？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.15,0:06:49.20,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,だとしたらムカつくわ。
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.28,0:06:51.87,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,つか戦士としての礼儀ってもんが…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.99,0:06:56.08,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,その者…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.12,0:06:58.87,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,他に何かしましたか？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.71,0:07:01.33,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,名はなんといいますか？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.42,0:07:04.17,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,な…名前は言えねェ…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.96,0:07:06.96,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,やっぱ
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.05,0:07:11.30,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,ワケわからんちん同士でひかれるものがあるんだなー。
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.39,0:07:14.35,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,その野郎も妙なこと言ってたぜ
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.43,0:07:17.93,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,“本当の戦士に剣は要らない”
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.02,0:07:19.35,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,とかなんとか…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.61,0:07:31.49,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,え？な、なになに？坊主。
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.57,0:07:34.32,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,お、おい。ちょ…ど、どこ行くんだよおい。え？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.04,0:07:41.04,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,なんなんだよ坊主よォ。
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.12,0:07:43.63,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,今のはあたりか？“アイ”か？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.72,0:07:57.18,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,戦士…本当の…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.72,0:07:59.93,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,剣は必要ない…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.69,0:08:09.74,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,本当の…戦士…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.91,0:08:25.42,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,天気の文句を私に言われても困りますよ。
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.17,0:08:29.63,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,私ゃ船乗りですよ？海ならともかく、
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.71,0:08:32.59,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,陸の天気なんぞ専門外でしてね。
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.18,0:08:36.68,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,冬の入りっぱなにこんなに積もることを予想しろってほうが
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.76,0:08:38.06,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,無茶ですよ
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.76,0:08:41.85,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,そんなことは言うとらん。ワシは今、
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.93,0:08:45.60,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,貴様からツキが離れとることを言うておるのだ。
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.77,0:08:49.48,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,雪に焦って進路を変えた途端これじゃ。
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.57,0:08:52.82,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,貴様の兵も少なからず動揺しておるぞ
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.90,0:08:56.99,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,私の手下は修羅場をくぐってきてるンです。
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.24,0:09:00.29,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,この程度のことじゃビクビクしませんよ。
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.66,0:09:03.71,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,命令どおりにスラスラッと動いてるでしょ？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.08,0:09:10.55,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,引き返せ。マーシア横断は無理じゃ
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.46,0:09:16.59,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,雪をこいで進むんなら、戦利品は捨てねばなりません。
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.97,0:09:18.64,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,手下どもは納得しないでしょう。
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.81,0:09:21.10,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,どちらにしろ
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.18,0:09:23.48,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,今夜は露営は無理です
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.40,0:09:27.60,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,アシェラッド。
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.69,0:09:29.69,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,準備万端だ。
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.77,0:09:31.11,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,いけるぜ
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.19,0:09:32.23,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,よし
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.07,0:09:35.24,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,アシェラッド…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.49,0:09:38.37,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,ツキの落ちとる時は
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.45,0:09:40.74,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,何をやっても裏目に出るぞ
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.83,0:09:42.16,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,ラグナル殿。
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.20,0:09:46.58,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,何をそんなにためらわれるのです？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.09,0:09:53.21,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,村邑の襲撃、略奪は…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.13,0:09:56.63,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,我らノルド人の伝統でしょう？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.64,0:10:07.31,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,天におわします我らの父よ
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.56,0:10:11.57,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,私たちの日ごとの糧を今日もお与え下さい
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.82,0:10:14.40,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,私たちが罪人を赦すように、
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.48,0:10:16.70,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,私たちの罪をお赦し下さい
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.74,0:10:19.36,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,誘惑に遭わせず、
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.45,0:10:22.03,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,悪よりお救い下さい
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.12,0:10:24.29,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,国と力と栄えとは限りなく、
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.37,0:10:26.75,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,あなたのものです
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.62,0:10:28.67,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,アーメン
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.75,0:10:30.00,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,アーメン
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.92,0:10:37.76,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,ねーお父ちゃーん。
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.38,0:10:41.01,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,どーしていつもおいのりするのー？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.35,0:10:46.02,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,イエス様がそうしろとおっしゃったからさ。
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.10,0:10:48.35,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,イエス様の言うことに間違いはない
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.73,0:10:51.52,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,おいのりしないとどーなるの？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.61,0:10:56.11,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,そりゃお前、不信心者は死んでから地獄におちるんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.19,0:10:57.53,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,そうだ。
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.61,0:11:01.87,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,地獄は悪魔がウーヨウヨいるこわ～い所だぞぉ。
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.95,0:11:04.03,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,いやだろぉ悪魔
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.45,0:11:07.29,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,アクマこわい…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.37,0:11:09.29,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,ん。父ちゃんもこわい。
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.87,0:11:13.79,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,でもお祈りする良い子は天国へ行ける。
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.88,0:11:15.30,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,よく覚えておきなさい
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.59,0:11:20.88,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,なんかピンとこないなぁ…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.18,0:11:25.51,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,もうじきみんな、天国か地獄に連れてかれるなんて
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.60,0:11:29.23,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,家族がバラバラになったらイヤだわねェ
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.31,0:11:31.10,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,でもお父ちゃん。
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.19,0:11:35.36,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,どうして神様は急にこの世をお裁きになろうとするの？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.65,0:11:37.23,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,急じゃないぞ。
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.32,0:11:39.61,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,大昔から決められてたんだ。
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.69,0:11:43.57,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,イエス様が復活なさってから千年後ってな
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.70,0:11:46.83,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,つまり20年後
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.08,0:11:57.30,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,神様のお裁きで悪党はみーんな地獄行きだ
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.96,0:11:59.13,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,オレしってるゥ！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.21,0:12:01.09,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,あくとうはでーんじん！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.17,0:12:03.59,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,おぉ！あいつら超ワル！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.05,0:12:07.43,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,きっと神様はああいう連中がわいてくるのを
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.51,0:12:09.35,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,ご存じだったんだろうな。
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.89,0:12:14.23,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,いいか、お前たちはイエス様のいいつけをよ～く守って…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.19,0:12:16.19,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,アン
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.65,0:12:19.78,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,おしっこ！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.62,0:12:32.58,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,どうしようどうしよう！？悪魔こわいよーっ！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.73,0:12:56.31,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,でもステキ…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.73,0:12:59.36,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,またはめちゃった…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.82,0:13:03.70,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,いくらするんだろう、この指輪…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.78,0:13:05.86,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,今からでもお金払ったら
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.95,0:13:08.49,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,神様はゆるしてくれるかしら…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.83,0:13:16.50,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,きっとあれは悪魔が誘惑したんだわ
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.84,0:13:27.09,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,お金もないのに市場見物なんかするんじゃなかった…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.10,0:13:32.43,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,アタシみたいな悪い子は
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.52,0:13:35.77,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,きっと裁きの日に地獄へおちるんだわ…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.02,0:13:40.94,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,きっと家族の中でアタシだけ…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.36,0:13:44.07,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,天国に行けないんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.83,0:14:00.46,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,うわああああん！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.54,0:14:03.46,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,左手にはめてもステキー！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.47,0:14:11.47,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,誰…？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.52,0:14:17.94,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,なんだよその顔ー！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.94,0:14:21.98,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,あー！アタシも！アタシもォー！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.15,0:14:25.74,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,さっきの話を聞いてなかったのかァ？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.82,0:14:28.70,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,ちゃんと良い子にしてないと神様が罰を…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.20,0:14:37.12,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,ちィーす！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.21,0:14:38.96,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,晩ゴハン拝見ー！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.51,0:14:49.93,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,みなさァん！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.01,0:14:51.85,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,逃げて下さーい！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.93,0:14:55.10,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,この村は狙われて…あ！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.18,0:14:56.18,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,デーン人が
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.27,0:14:57.89,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,この村を！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.10,0:15:00.19,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,死にてぇのか！！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.32,0:15:09.45,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,あったけー。生き返るわー
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.53,0:15:12.32,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,なんだ。ここンちはガキが多いな
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.16,0:15:17.29,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,なんだねアンタたちゃ突然…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.37,0:15:20.75,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,大麦のミルクがゆと干し肉が少々…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.83,0:15:22.92,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,チッ、玉ネギ入ってる
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.84,0:15:26.38,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,おい。武器になりそうなモンおさえとけ
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.46,0:15:27.46,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,おう
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.39,0:15:38.64,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,まっじぃ…ヒデェもん食ってんなオイ！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.31,0:15:43.90,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,ちょっと！なんなのあなた！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.98,0:15:45.57,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,食べ物を粗末にして！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.65,0:15:47.86,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,バチがあた…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.07,0:15:56.12,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,大丈夫かオイ！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.20,0:15:59.83,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,えーとなんだっけ？イングランド語で
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.91,0:16:02.04,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,クイモノゼンブ
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.12,0:16:04.33,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,あー。そーそー
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.42,0:16:07.21,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,なぁ！おい！\Nおいオッさん。コラ
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.01,0:16:14.43,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,クイモノゼンブダセ。コロスゾ
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.44,0:16:25.61,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,こんだけか？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.73,0:16:31.53,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,ガキは2人で1人前として50人。
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.61,0:16:34.78,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,てことは冬越しの食料も50人分か…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.75,0:16:43.21,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,104人の戦士には足りねェな
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.00,0:16:48.84,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,どうしようどうしよう…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.92,0:16:51.84,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,みんな捕まっちゃった…どうしよう
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.01,0:16:57.35,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,神父よォー！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.81,0:17:02.10,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,あんたは王子殿下の教師で、
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.18,0:17:04.60,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,一応この兵団の客だ。
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.90,0:17:07.52,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,一度だけ許す。
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.61,0:17:09.86,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,だが次ジャマをすれば
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.94,0:17:11.65,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,その場で殺す。
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.90,0:17:15.28,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,オレァもともと坊主は嫌ェなんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.20,0:17:20.12,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,あっ…あんたたちゃ…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.70,0:17:23.50,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,デーン人か？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.58,0:17:26.33,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,ワシらの言葉の通じる者はおらんか？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.22,0:17:38.34,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,頼む！食べる物を半分！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.43,0:17:41.18,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,せめて半分残してくれないか！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.26,0:17:44.18,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,半分あればなんとか冬は越せる！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.06,0:17:50.73,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,赤ん坊もおるんだ！どうかっ！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.69,0:17:55.57,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,赤ん坊か。そりゃ大変だなァ
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.24,0:18:03.20,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,大丈夫。あんた方のことは考えてあるよ。
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.29,0:18:06.21,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,冬越しの心配はしなくていい
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.67,0:18:09.71,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,本当にッ…本当にか！？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.25,0:18:11.67,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,本当さ。
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.30,0:18:16.42,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,来年も再来年も、もう冬越しの心配はいらん
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.55,0:18:20.51,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,あんた方を苦悩から解放してやろう
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.93,0:18:29.52,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,アシェラッド…彼らは非戦闘員だ…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.19,0:18:34.73,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,生かしておいてもこいつらに食わすメシはねェ
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.90,0:18:37.45,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,ひとりでも脱走されたら
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.53,0:18:40.45,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,敵地の真ん中でモタついてることをチクられる。
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.53,0:18:42.37,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,そいつはいただけねェ
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.66,0:18:46.00,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,どうだ？穴は掘れたか？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.08,0:18:49.58,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,オゥ！詰めれば62人入るぜ
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.67,0:18:50.71,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,アシェラッド！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.42,0:18:53.80,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,この者たちはキリスト教徒だ！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.59,0:18:56.09,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,だからなんスか。
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.71,0:19:00.18,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,王子殿下の御為にはこれが最善ですよ
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.64,0:19:01.64,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,ハイ
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.76,0:19:03.22,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,他に質問のある方は？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.56,0:19:06.02,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,いないね
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.27,0:19:07.43,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,よし！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.68,0:19:08.77,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,そんじゃ野郎ども
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.65,0:19:12.77,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,殺れ
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.84,0:21:00.09,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,神様…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.88,0:21:06.47,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,見ていらっしゃいます…か…？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.31,0:21:17.77,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,父ちゃんや…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.86,0:21:20.32,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,母ちゃん…じいちゃん…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.40,0:21:22.40,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,弟や妹はっ…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.82,0:21:28.99,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,そちらに着きましたか？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.92,0:21:48.05,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,やっぱりアタシのことはお召しにならないのですね
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.51,0:21:50.72,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,そうよね…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.89,0:21:53.39,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,だってアタシ…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.69,0:21:58.60,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,ドキドキしてるんだもの
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.19,0:22:06.82,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,あんなにも…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.90,0:22:10.66,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,あんなにも、悪い人たちがいるなんて…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.99,0:22:13.70,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,あんなにも…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.79,0:22:17.12,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,あなたの罰をおそれない人たちがいるなんて…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.04,0:22:24.17,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,指輪を盗んだあの瞬間みたいに…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.38,0:22:27.97,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,アタシは今…！
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.01,0:22:33.68,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,ドキドキしてるの…
